            "title": "虚拟号码提供商接收（发送）短信（Twilio 及其替代品）",
            "summary": "<p class=\"entry-title full-title\" data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\"><span style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\">网络已经成为隐私的噩梦，其原因之一就是太多网站乐于要求用户提供电话号码。所以，我自然而然地开始寻找获取其他号码的方法。</span></p>\n",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"entry-title full-title\" data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\"><span style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\">网络已经成为隐私的噩梦，其原因之一就是太多网站乐于要求用户提供电话号码。所以，我自然而然地开始寻找获取其他号码的方法。</span></p>\n\n<div class=\"entry-content full-content\" data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\">\n<p data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">声明</span>，几乎所有的MVNO运营商（如Twilio）都对接受入站OTP（即短信验证码）有严格的风控，通常是全部拦截并提示滥用风险（试多了会封号）。而出站短信的部分也是严格风控（群发/bulk SMS），且通常只允许作为通知类短信/广告/物流推送等合理合规用途。</p>\n<h2 data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\">Twilio</h2>\n<ul data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\">\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">号码月费：1美元/月</span></span></span></li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">发送短信：0.0075 美元 + 运营商费用（0.002 美元至 0.005 美元）</span></span></span></li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">接收短信：$0.0075</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-inline-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-inline-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">Vonage</span></span></span></h2>\n<ul data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\">\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-