ve-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">接收短信：$0.0067</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\">Plivo</h2>\n<ul data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\">\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">号码月费：0.50 美元/月（原价 0.80 美元）</span></span></span></li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">发送短信：0.0050 美元 + 运营商费用（0.0025 美元至 0.0050 美元）</span></span></span></li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">接收短信：$0 + 运营商费用（$0 至 $0.005）</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-inline-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-inline-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">Bandwitch</span></span></span></h2>\n<ul data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\">\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">号码月费：0.35美元/月</span></span></span></li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">发送短信：0.0040 美元 + 运营商费用 （0.0020 美元至 0.0050 美元）</span></span></span></li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-wrapper\" lang=\"zh-CN\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper-theme-none immersive-translate-target-translation-block-wrapper\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\"><span class=\"notranslate immersive-translate-target-inner immersive-translate-target-translation-theme-none-inner\" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark=\"1\">接收短信：$0 + 运营商费用（$0 至 $0.003）</span></span></span></li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\">每月最低消费3000$</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\">Sinch</h2>\n<ul data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\">\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\">客制化价格</li>\n<li data-immersive-translate-walked=\"019c3860-a5a2-4c9a-97fa-92fbbecd68cf\" data-immersive-translate-paragraph=\"1\">有最低消费</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这些并不是全部，我只是罗列出了一些比较有代表性的MVNO虚拟运营商，希望这会对你有所启发。</p>\n</div>",
